    <title>
        <en>Everything Constructable</en>
        <de>Alles Baubar</de>
        <fr>Tout Constructible</fr>
    </title>
    <description>
        <en><![CDATA[Everything Constructable

Transforms building placement into a multi-phase construction process. Instead of buildings appearing instantly, placing a building will:

1. Flatten the terrain as normal
2. Place a construction fence around the site
3. Create a construction project that spans multiple months
4. Charge only an initial deposit

Construction projects can run in two modes:
- Automatic: Monthly charges are deducted and the build progresses each month
- Wait for Resources: Deliver materials (wood beams, planks, cement, etc.) to advance each phase

Approach a construction site on foot to view progress, change mode, or cancel for a partial refund.

Fully supports multiplayer.
]]></en>
    </description>
